description:
The Second Coming is an event that is mentioned over 2500 in the Bible and was to be kept at the forefront of our minds, our teaching and our outreach but it had been lost sight of in the middle ages in the church. This chapter outlines how prophetic fulfillment in the 1700's and 1800's helped to publicise this belief and make both Christians and non-Christians think about it and plan for it again!
